column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "2B521A04455FCE44AE060DA4FDC10FB2", "It\'s all cool here. Good luck.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "FA7427B14E48B2AE58B9CFB787CD702C", "I must help, too. I\'ll go back and forth between here and the city whenever I can.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "72C459E440DF11F96841688F8A227AD8", "Andromon joins the city!")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "AEE67D8149E90C06F04CC1B26188F65A", "Data repair is complete. Now, let\'s read data.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "57C6F495412880642C6D93BBA90F894E", "One hundred years ago, Analog Humans appeared on Digimon island.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "EE4C51BC447041DB791D9C992DA523ED", "Analog Humans and native Digimon fought very hard.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "BE5029DC45A59784AC46069EB94539AE", "After ten years of battle, the Analog Humans were defeated and disappeared.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "C26415B04E2C54470CFB059F5F09DBAC", "In the next ten years, mysteriously, the island\'s area almost doubled in size.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "28375FD64B94A324A6F3FDB55CDD1708", "So humans fought Digimon?")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "33F59EA544DBD43CEBD89392388D7DB2", "I\'m sorry. That\'s all the data we could recover.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "3053CD16434DBEEA544C9186552D737F", "Don\'t worry. This is very important information. Now I know so much more.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "61B6A4B4419563657A2593AD640A024D", "These humans are probably the ones who caused confusion and trouble on the island.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "46E8ED69433E5207DD5C0BBF9A5745DD", "Can humans live one hundred years?")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "A960CF9940D57A089D16D6988495D49C", "It seems that for humans, time is slow in this world.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "A6AFC03A428E39CFF990178DF9928E98", "I guess that\'s why I don\'t have to eat or sleep here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "819FE5EB41217DABAD5563BECA1BA580", "One hundred years is a very long time. Those guys must be very tough.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "46B9ACC54C8A1D61655325B3A581EEF3", "Do you think they are hiding somewhere?")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "8E687B07400953A0CC3B5DB4B71E25F3", "I\'ll find them and do something.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "3094525245D2E9491FD8B5987499F437", "Now I know why I\'m here. Since I\'m human, I need to deal with them.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "3863D47C409C26E2B12456A8C9B41DBC", "We\'re so sorry. We\'ll close the factory for a while.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "2948785342D92757A2489A9546AE2F80", "Because of the trouble now, no one can say what\'s gonna happen. It\'s not your fault.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "9560B07541FD4C947739879890BE6EA5", "I think there\'s somebody controlling Giromon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "7C11E24949C100CF7454B986F1083283", "Computers were destroyed and waste water started to leak.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "5F2DC51F405883B9F9154CB1CF157E72", "That water made Digimons insane. I don\'t think it\'s a coincidence.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "34707DC648C59C7BFF6ECD9FB560E921", "These computers have some key importance.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "F7414B5541CA07F2A06FF3B3222577B4", "It may be too late, but I think someone was trying to get us.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "F91007ED4BE73BDE73115A95D130911B", "I think there was some data regarding the island\'s past on these computers.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "2F70C9294E4B4A12D3C016B17069EFAF", "But due to the Giromon\'s riot, the data was destroyed.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "808DAA2A4AADCE70A73165B41B31F904", "You\'ve never seen the data?")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "7FE008284091225342EFB1B4DCBD44BE", "No, but we might be able to repair some of it. I\'ll try to connect the data.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "5A65D4E9483FFC4CEED6E2A2BFBDE245", "I see, thank you. How long will it take?")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "5DBC3EEB45698EF767F313BCCA138D8A", "It\'ll be a while. I\'ll reopen the town entrance, so come back again.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "8F575ED44B6CD2F22D159CA07D5163A0", "Thanks. I\'ll be back.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "97704BB54700B8D50D337B84F30F913F", "Have you finish repairing the data?")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "D72505434D6506F452B8BB89329A0016", "It\'ll take a while longer. Come back again.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "7830B2A4486D62E4E0B5D9AE66C4340B", "I have to apologize.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "9EE90E874FF9131296A390B271E9F19C", "Do that later, you gotta stop the factory\'s machines now!")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "83BBC2834C48756EE8ED2C93F0DF63FD", "Alright, I will.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "6B2713E14181519178856487DA7BE99D", "The factory\'s function has just stopped.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "4547B3E74AC9DAEA1D6400A56E560B1A", "Good, I\'ll check the sewer. Laters, dude.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "A472047F469E0D44F33905A47CC4A30B", "I must apologize.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "F7EF7C4C4E3BB93D7D7803841A6DAFB3", "We don\'t got time to discuss that now!")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "C634E1914FD9A7C37AACF88F428C695C", "Our computer is perfect.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "3C1879364E9D4C2893E97BB326EF9C02", "Is the factory really safe? What can we do now?")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "CEE1956747033ED4A5A005996FDF5986", "Ok, we gotta do something about the guards. We don\'t have any other way!")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "3650F2F94A6D5D757265AB918985AC16", "How did you get into town?")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "78E14A3C4B650583139A2E98230F517C", "If you don\'t have any business here, leave now!")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "2E2DADF3492D36568ADC37A857FAB5D1", "We can talk about that later. I gotta check out the factory now.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "901F435641E46FA645EBA0AFE5AE3770", "This is a life and death situation. Give me the okay!")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "35B7FF9E4D90D92F5960C1973FE16D2F", "I don\'t quite understand what you\'re trying to do. I can\'t give you permission.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "E55803F04B700F3EB13F01B0C903A41F", "There are Digimon about to fade away because of the waste water from the factory!")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "FB17BA89417EF462F9FAC2ABF4F45483", "From the factory? No way! The waste water cleaning system is working fine.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "24E2C3B7452A7D9620075C9CC43960C7", "How can you know it\'s working fine if we don\'t check?!")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "F9D85CD34B2077A60E67F296E99745AB", "Our computer is perfect. In emergencies, the Net Keeper will shut down the system.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "C55D79264A51B5350E4AC79D2C959891", "Are you telling me that Net Keeper will always work correctly?")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "AF93588945D8BA252BB9048C35E2B210", "Net Keeper is another name for Giromon who is an Ultimate Digimon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "9F324CB246453C273289C19A89A1F4A5", "His judgement and ability are so perfect.")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "B328EDDE44461EDEE17656AC375E2A4B", "He is a Digimon?! Oh no, we are in even more trouble now. Please, give me permission!")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "CAF561674609B83BC86295AACA6BEE4E", "Leave! Now!")
NSLOCTEXT("[406AD34540B72144186E909E481A6BB2]", "537BF67248E21A546DEFA3860FAEEA1A", "Sigh...Rats!")
